    "description": "Iron Conflict是一款多人在线公平竞技的即时战术游戏。高度模拟二战至今坦克、火炮、战机、导弹车等多类真实武装载具，侦察、突袭、支援……特色鲜明且互有克制。面对复杂的作战地形，玩家可随心组合单位，搭配功能迥异的配件，采用灵活的战术和操作技巧，与敌军展开空地一体的烈火战争角逐！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各具风格的真实武装</h2>精确模拟了二战至今多个国家、百余种经典武装载具，功能定位涵盖潜入侦察、强攻突进、空中打击、远程支援等方面，并且基于真实战场表现，单位之间还存在完整的克制体系。无论是99A2主战坦克，还是F-22隐身战斗机，在这里你都可以真实操控。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/e062d91b58c39d6ffe50d508db998a82.poster.avif?t=1687299623\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/e062d91b58c39d6ffe50d508db998a82.webm?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/e062d91b58c39d6ffe50d508db998a82.mp4?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵活多变的战术配合</h2>掌握视野意味着主动权在手，因此构建陆、空联合侦察体系至关重要。共享“眼位”视野可以实时洞察战场动态，无论是主动绕后突袭，又或是指引友军远程火力支援，快速调整战术高效制敌。此外单位还可以选配合适的配件，差异化的阵容塑造更将带来无限可能。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/a0da3109aa7c72d6a718ebaa5ddbf1d2.poster.avif?t=1687299623\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/a0da3109aa7c72d6a718ebaa5ddbf1d2.webm?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/a0da3109aa7c72d6a718ebaa5ddbf1d2.mp4?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不尽相同的操作乐趣</h2>你可以根据个人喜好，或者阵容互补需求，挑选3个单位组建战术小队。这其中“东风快递”爱好者可以借助己方视野，远程开镜锁定目标，预判走位精准打击；或者操控轻型坦克，凭借机动优势和微操技巧以弱胜强，这些单位间的特性差异造就了不同的操作乐趣。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/87ac88f318ffd447247e826f3b7b8c1f.poster.avif?t=1687299623\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/87ac88f318ffd447247e826f3b7b8c1f.webm?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/87ac88f318ffd447247e826f3b7b8c1f.mp4?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逼真复杂的战场环境</h2>山丘平原、城镇废墟、戈壁沙漠等地图风格迥异，在虚幻4引擎的技术支持下，战场地貌细节、物理破坏效果更趋近真实。在这里桥梁、树林、河流、建筑等等既可能是阻碍，也可能是助力，争夺抢占战略关卡，巧妙利用地形优势痛击敌军。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/ba6ac16183bc3fc59e4b1f6db9ca4b19.poster.avif?t=1687299623\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/ba6ac16183bc3fc59e4b1f6db9ca4b19.webm?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371480/extras/ba6ac16183bc3fc59e4b1f6db9ca4b19.mp4?t=1687299623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
